/>\n<br />\n巴士業職工會聯盟<br />\n3小時<br />\n<br />\n【巴職聯回應 2月3日政府防疫記者會】<br />\n<br />\n香港政府的防疫措施至今仍落後於其他地方；直至今日傍晚的記者會，特首林鄭月娥繼續拒絕「全面封關」，只將人流集中經深圳灣口岸及港珠澳大橋口岸入境，新措施直接增加對巴士前線人員的威脅!<br />\n<br />\n本聯盟認為，香港政府必須果斷執行「全面封關」，限制任何國藉的旅客經中國疫區入境來港，堵截隱性患者將武漢肺炎病毒輸入境內，從以確保醫療資源能應付本港的抗疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n假如醫護界罷工未能打動政府「拒絕全面封關」之決定，就保障業界從業員健康及公眾利益著想；本聯盟將開展籌備緊急會員大會表決通過罷工 / 工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n巴士業職工會聯盟<br />\n2020年2月3日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0VFx9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0VFx9W.jpg&h=5b252a0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69080a154f0fb23da94fddbdd90e7964471d8a0a","tid":1861162,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03ae01c37a1b5833cf4a989281d6e6b68d5ece9","tid":1861162,"uid":217450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"政治家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c276ccac54b82f9deff2f3ec8f39fa476433bc","tid":1861162,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e03ae01c37a1b5833cf4a989281d6e6b68d5ece9","tid":1861162,"uid":217450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"re